trans-unit.source: Serves as the primary control in the Web Parts control set for hosting <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls on a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Fungerer som den primære kontrollen i webdeler kontrollen som er angitt for vert <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> vises på en webside.

trans-unit.source: In the Web Parts feature, a zone is a defined region on a Web page that contains Web Parts controls.
trans-unit.target: I funksjonen webdeler er en sone et angitt område på en side som inneholder webdeler kontroller.

trans-unit.source: The primary functions of a zone are to lay out the controls it contains, and to provide a common user interface (UI) for those controls.
trans-unit.target: De primære funksjonene i en sone er å sette opp Kontroller den inneholder, og oppgi en vanlig brukergrensesnittet (UI) for kontrollene.

trans-unit.source: For general information about zones and how they are used in Web Parts applications, see the reference documentation for the base <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> classes, and the topic entitled [Web Parts Control Set Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha generell informasjon om soner og hvordan de brukes i webdeler programmer, kan du se referansedokumentasjonen for grunntallet <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>klasser og emnet krav [deler kontrollen angitt oversikt over Web](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone>

trans-unit.source: The special function of the WebPartZone control is to contain <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls, which form the main UI of Web Parts applications.
trans-unit.target: Funksjonen spesielle kontrollens webdel-sone som inneholder <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller, som utgjør primære Brukergrensesnittet for webdeler programmene.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: A WebPartZone control can be declared in persistence format on a Web page, enabling developers to use it as a template and to add other server controls within the `<asp:webpartzone>` element.
trans-unit.target: En webdel-sone kontroll kan deklareres i utholdenhet format på en side, aktiverer utviklere å bruke den som en mal og legge til andre serverkontroller i den `<asp:webpartzone>` elementet.

trans-unit.source: Any type of server control, if added to a WebPartZone zone, can function as a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control at run time.
trans-unit.target: Alle typer serverkontroll, hvis lagt til en webdel-sone sone, som kan fungere som en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll på kjøretidspunktet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: This is true regardless of whether the added control is a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, a user control, a custom control, or an ASP.NET control.
trans-unit.target: Dette er sant uansett om tillagt kontrollen er en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll, en kontroll, en egendefinert kontroll eller en ASP.NET-kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the topic for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart> class.
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon, se emnet for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart>

trans-unit.source: Besides containing <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls, a WebPartZone control also provides a common UI for the controls it contains.
trans-unit.target: I tillegg som inneholder <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller, en webdel-sone kontroll gir deg også et felles brukergrensesnitt for Kontroller den inneholder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: This common UI, known collectively as chrome, consists of the peripheral UI elements on all the controls, such as the border, title, header and footer, style characteristics, and verbs (UI actions that a user can carry out on a control, such as close or minimize).
trans-unit.target: Vanlig Praksis, kjent samlet kalles chrome, består av eksterne UI-elementer i alle kontrollene, for eksempel kantlinje, tittel, topptekst og bunntekst, stilen og verb (UI handlinger som en bruker kan utføre på en kontroll, slik som lukke eller minimere).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Internet Explorer might render the height of a WebPartZone or its contained controls in an unexpected way, depending on the orientation of the zone.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Internet Explorer kan gjengi høyden på en webdel-sone eller de inneholder kontrollene på en uventet måte, avhengig av retningen på sonen.

trans-unit.source: For more details, see the documentation for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.LayoutOrientation%2A> or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Height%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, kan du se dokumentasjonen for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.LayoutOrientation%2A>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Height%2A>Egenskaper.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.Height%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.LayoutOrientation%2A>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZone class derives most of its behavior from the base <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> classes; it adds only one unique member, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Webdel-sone klassen er avledet de fleste av virkemåten grunntallet <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase>klasser; bare én unik medlem, legges det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone.ZoneTemplate%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone.ZoneTemplate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebZone>

trans-unit.source: This property references an <xref:System.Web.UI.ITemplate> object, which is a template that allows page developers to define the controls in a zone statically by using a `<zonetemplate>` element in the declarative markup of an .aspx page.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen refererer til en <xref:System.Web.UI.ITemplate>-objektet som er en mal som gjør det mulig for utviklere siden for å definere kontrollene i en sone statisk ved hjelp av en `<zonetemplate>` elementet i den deklarerende markup av .aspx-siden.</xref:System.Web.UI.ITemplate>

trans-unit.source: Accessibility The markup rendered by default for this control might not conform to accessibility standards such as the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines 1.0 (WCAG) priority 1 guidelines.
trans-unit.target: Tilgjengelighet markup gjengis som standard for denne kontrollen, kan ikke med kravene for tilgjengelighet standarder som Web innhold tilgjengelighet retningslinjene 1.0 (WCAG) prioritet 1 retningslinjene.

trans-unit.source: For details about accessibility support for this control, see [ASP.NET Controls and Accessibility](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om tilgjengelighet støtte for denne kontrollen, kan du se [ASP.NET-kontroller og tilgjengelighet](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartZone method is a default constructor and does not set any values.
trans-unit.target: Angir ikke noen verdier metoden webdel-sone er en standardkonstruktør.

trans-unit.source: However, derived classes can use the constructor to set base zone properties, to create standard behaviors and appearance for a custom zone control.
trans-unit.target: Avledede klasser kan imidlertid bruke konstruktøren ikke angi egenskaper base sone, til å opprette standard virkemåter og utseendet for en egendefinert zone-kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Overrides the abstract base method and gets the initial set of static <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls contained within the zone's template.
trans-unit.target: Overstyrer abstrakt base metoden og henter det første settet med statiske <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller innenfor mal for den sonen.

trans-unit.source: The GetInitialWebParts method provides an implementation of the abstract base <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.GetInitialWebParts%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetInitialWebParts gir en implementering av den abstrakte basen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.GetInitialWebParts%2A>metode.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.GetInitialWebParts%2A>

trans-unit.source: The base method provides no implementation, but declares the method so that derived classes can customize how they will get the initial set of controls that belong in a zone, without taking personalization changes into account.
trans-unit.target: Metoden base gir ingen implementering, men deklarerer metoden slik at avledede klasser kan tilpasse hvordan de får første settet med kontroller som hører til i en sone, uten å ta tilpassing endringer i kontoen.

trans-unit.source: For each server control found in the zone, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateWebPart%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: For hver serverkontroll funnet i sonen i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateWebPart%2A>-metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.CreateWebPart%2A>

trans-unit.source: If a control inherits directly from the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> class, it is simply added to the zone's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.WebParts%2A> collection (and to the similar collection of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control).
trans-unit.target: Hvis en kontroll arver direkte fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>klassen det bare er lagt til i sonen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.WebParts%2A>samlingen (og lignende-samlingen for det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZoneBase.WebParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: If a control does not inherit directly from <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>, the Web Parts control set wraps the control with a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart> object, which enables the control to behave as a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control at run time.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en kontroll ikke arver direkte fra <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>, webdeler kontrollen settet bryter kontrollen med en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart>objektet, som aktiverer kontrollen skal fungere som en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroll på kjøretidspunktet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.GenericWebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> class implements the base method by returning the set of controls (if any) that are statically declared within a set of `<zonetemplate>` tags in the markup of a Web Parts page.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>klassen implementerer metoden base ved å returnere settet med kontroller (Hvis noen) som statisk er angitt i et sett med `<zonetemplate>` koder i koden for en webdeler side.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: If a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PlaceHolder> control is declared in a zone, the child controls of that control are added, rather than the control itself.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PlaceHolder>kontrollen er deklarert i en sone, barnet kontroller for at kontrollen legges til, i stedet for selve kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.PlaceHolder>

trans-unit.source: This implementation allows you to, for example, create a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> zone in a master page, and then declare individual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> or server controls in a content page.
trans-unit.target: Denne implementeringen lar deg, for eksempel opprette en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>sone i en hoveddokumentet og deklarere individuelle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>eller serverkontroller i et innhold.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: If you declare <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> controls in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> zone, they are ignored.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du angir <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>Kontroller i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>sone, de ignoreres.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The initial collection of controls returned by the GetInitialWebParts method might be different from the actual run-time collection of controls in a zone, after personalization has taken place.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Første samlingen av kontroller returnert av metoden GetInitialWebParts kan være forskjellig fra faktiske kjøretid samlingen av kontroller i en sone når personlige data har funnet sted.

trans-unit.source: For example, suppose you have a Web page with two <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> controls, and the first one contains user control named `User1` that is statically declared within the `<zonetemplate>` tags.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel anta at du har en side med to <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>kontroller, og den første som inneholder brukerkontrollen `User1` som statisk er deklarert i den `<zonetemplate>` koder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: If a user loads the page and drags `User1` into the second zone, then `User1` is still part of the collection that is returned by calling the GetInitialWebParts method for the first zone, because it is declared in that zone.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en bruker laster siden og drags `User1` i andre sone, `User1` fortsatt er en del av samlingen som returneres ved å kalle metoden GetInitialWebParts for første sonen, fordi den er deklarert i den sonen.

trans-unit.source: But at run time, when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control loads the personalization data, `User1` actually appears in the second zone where the user dragged it.
trans-unit.target: Men ved kjøretid, når den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>kontrollen laster inn personlige data `User1` vises i tidssone der brukeren drar den.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection"></xref> that contains all the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> or other server controls contained in the zone's template.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartCollection"> </xref> som inneholder alle de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> eller andre serverkontroller i mal for den sonen.

trans-unit.source: Overrides the base method to indicate that the zone has successfully been registered with the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Overstyrer base-metoden til å angi at sonen ble er registrert i <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.EventArgs> that contains the event data.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.EventArgs>som inneholder Hendelsesdata.</xref:System.EventArgs>

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a reference to an <xref href="System.Web.UI.ITemplate"></xref> instance that contains the controls declared in the markup of a Web page.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en referanse til en <xref href="System.Web.UI.ITemplate"> </xref> -forekomst som inneholder kontroller deklarert i koden for en webside.

trans-unit.source: The ZoneTemplate property refers to an <xref:System.Web.UI.ITemplate> instance within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> control.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ZoneTemplate refererer til en <xref:System.Web.UI.ITemplate>serverforekomsten i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.ITemplate>

trans-unit.source: The template contains static server controls that you can declare within a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> control, including <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls, user controls, custom controls, and ASP.NET controls.
trans-unit.target: Malen inneholder statisk serverkontroller du kan angi i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>kontrollere, inkludert <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>kontroller, brukerkontroller, egendefinerte kontroller og ASP.NET-kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>

trans-unit.source: When you add static <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> or other server controls to a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> in the declarative markup of a Web page, you must place the tags for the controls within a pair of `<zonetemplate>` tags.
trans-unit.target: Når du legger til statiske <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>eller andre serverkontroller til en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone>i deklarerende koden for en webside, må du sette koder for kontroller med et par `<zonetemplate>` koder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartZone> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: If you do not declare the controls within `<zonetemplate>` tags, an exception is thrown.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke deklarere kontrollene i `<zonetemplate>` koder, et unntak.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.ITemplate"></xref> that contains the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls in a zone.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.ITemplate"> </xref> som inneholder den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller i en sone.

trans-unit.source: Registration of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls in the zone is already complete.
trans-unit.target: Registrering av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> kontroller i sonen er allerede fullført.
